trans-unit.source: Represents a field that displays navigation controls in a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager"></xref> control enable users to page through data.
trans-unit.target: Representerar ett fält som visar navigeringskontroller i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager"> </xref> kontroll användarna med data.

trans-unit.source: The NextPreviousPagerField class represents a field that displays navigation controls in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager> control.
trans-unit.target: Klassen NextPreviousPagerField representerar ett fält som visar navigeringskontroller i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager>

trans-unit.source: These navigation controls can be used to page through data that are displayed by a control that implements the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.IPageableItemContainer> interface, such as the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView> control.
trans-unit.target: Dessa navigeringskontroller kan användas till sidan med data som visas i en kontroll som implementerar den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.IPageableItemContainer>gränssnitt som den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.IPageableItemContainer>

trans-unit.source: The NextPreviousPagerField class provides buttons that enable users to navigate through the pages of data one page at a time, or to jump to the first or last page of data.
trans-unit.target: NextPreviousPagerField-klassen innehåller knappar som gör att användare kan navigera i sidorna i data med en sida i taget eller gå till den första eller sista sidan i data.

trans-unit.source: You can customize the appearance of the NextPreviousPagerField object by using the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ButtonCssClass%2A> property to set the style of the buttons.
trans-unit.target: Du kan anpassa utseendet på NextPreviousPagerField-objekt med hjälp av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ButtonCssClass%2A>egenskapen för att ange formatet på knapparna.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ButtonCssClass%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can also use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ButtonType%2A> property to choose the type of button that is displayed.
trans-unit.target: Du kan också använda den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ButtonType%2A>egenskapen för att välja vilken typ av knapp som visas.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ButtonType%2A>

trans-unit.source: The following table lists the available button types.
trans-unit.target: I följande tabell visas tillgängliga knapptyper.

trans-unit.source: |Button type|Description| |-----------------|-----------------| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonType>|A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Button> control.| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonType>|An <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageButton> control.| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonType>|A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton> control.| You can hide a NextPreviousPagerField object in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager> control by setting the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPagerField.Visible%2A> property to `false`.
trans-unit.target: | Knappen typen | Beskrivning | |-----------------|-----------------| | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonType>| En kontroll <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Button>. | | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonType>| En kontroll som <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageButton>. | | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonType>| En kontroll <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton>. | Du kan dölja ett NextPreviousPagerField objekt i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager>kontroll genom att ange den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPagerField.Visible%2A>egenskapen `false`.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPagerField.Visible%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonType> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageButton> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonType> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Button> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonType>

trans-unit.source: You can also hide the individual buttons (the first-page, previous-page, next-page, and last-page buttons) by setting the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ShowFirstPageButton%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ShowPreviousPageButton%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ShowNextPageButton%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ShowLastPageButton%2A> properties to `false`.
trans-unit.target: Du kan även dölja enskilda knapparna (första sida, föregående sida, nästa sida och sista sidan knappar) genom att ange den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ShowFirstPageButton%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ShowPreviousPageButton%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ShowNextPageButton%2A>, och <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ShowLastPageButton%2A>Egenskaper som `false`.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ShowLastPageButton%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ShowNextPageButton%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ShowPreviousPageButton%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ShowFirstPageButton%2A>

trans-unit.source: The NextPreviousPagerField control enables you to specify custom text for each button by using the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.FirstPageText%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.PreviousPageText%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.NextPageText%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.LastPageText%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollen NextPreviousPagerField kan du ange anpassade text för varje knapp med hjälp av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.FirstPageText%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.PreviousPageText%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.NextPageText%2A>, och <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.LastPageText%2A>Egenskaper.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.LastPageText%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.NextPageText%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.PreviousPageText%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.FirstPageText%2A>

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ButtonType%2A> property is set to `ButtonType.Image`, you must provide the URL to an image that will be displayed for the button.
trans-unit.target: När den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ButtonType%2A>egenskap är inställd på `ButtonType.Image`, du måste ange en URL till en bild som visas för knappen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ButtonType%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can set images individually for each button by setting the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.FirstPageImageUrl%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.PreviousPageImageUrl%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.NextPageImageUrl%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.LastPageImageUrl%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: Du kan ange bilder individuellt för varje knapp genom att ange den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.FirstPageImageUrl%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.PreviousPageImageUrl%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.NextPageImageUrl%2A>, och <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.LastPageImageUrl%2A>Egenskaper.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.LastPageImageUrl%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.NextPageImageUrl%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.PreviousPageImageUrl%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.FirstPageImageUrl%2A>

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ButtonType%2A> property is set to `ButtonType.Image`, the corresponding text property acts as the alternate text for the image.
trans-unit.target: När den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ButtonType%2A>egenskap är inställd på `ButtonType.Image`, egenskapen motsvarande fungerar som den alternativa texten för bilden.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ButtonType%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, the text that is specified by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.FirstPageText%2A> property is displayed as the alternate text for the first-page image button.
trans-unit.target: Till exempel den text som anges av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.FirstPageText%2A>egenskapen visas som den alternativa texten för knappen första sidan.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.FirstPageText%2A>

trans-unit.source: In browsers that support tooltips, this text is also displayed as a tooltip.
trans-unit.target: Den här texten visas även som en knappbeskrivning i webbläsare som stöder knappbeskrivningar.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the cascading style sheet (CSS) class that is used to render the buttons of the pager field on the browser.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger den övergripande (CSS) Formatmallsklass som används för att återge knapparna pager-fält i webbläsare.

trans-unit.source: Use the ButtonCssClass property to specify the CSS class to render on the browser for the buttons of the pager field.
trans-unit.target: Använd egenskapen ButtonCssClass för att ange CSS-klassen som ska renderas i webbläsaren för knapparna i sidindelningsfältet.

trans-unit.source: This property will always be rendered as the class attribute, regardless of the browser.
trans-unit.target: Den här egenskapen ska alltid renderas som class-attribut oavsett webbläsaren.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > On browsers that do not support CSS, setting the ButtonCssClass property has no effect.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > I webbläsare som inte stöder CSS ButtonCssClass-egenskapen har ingen effekt.

trans-unit.source: The value of this property is stored in viewstate.
trans-unit.target: Värdet för denna egenskap lagras i viewstate.

trans-unit.source: The CSS class used to render the buttons of the pager field on the client.
trans-unit.target: CSS-klassen för att återge knapparna sidindelningsfältet på klienten.

trans-unit.source: The default is an empty string, which indicates that the ButtonCssClass property is not set.
trans-unit.target: Standardvärdet är en tom sträng som anger att egenskapen ButtonCssClass inte har angetts.

trans-unit.source: Use the RenderDisabledButtonsAsLabels property to specify whether disabled buttons are rendered as <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Label> controls by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField> object.
trans-unit.target: Använd egenskapen RenderDisabledButtonsAsLabels för att ange om inaktiverad knapparna ska renderas som <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Label>styr av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField>objekt.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Label>

trans-unit.source: The buttons are disabled by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField> object when the function associated with the button cannot be performed.
trans-unit.target: Knapparna är inaktiverade som den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField>objekt när funktionen som är associerade med knappen inte kan utföras.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField>

trans-unit.source: For example, when you are in the first page of data, the first-page and previous-page buttons are disabled.
trans-unit.target: När du är på den första sidan i data inaktiveras exempelvis knapparna första sida och föregående sida.

trans-unit.source: By default, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField> object renders the disabled buttons by using the control type specified by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ButtonType%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Som standard den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField>objekt visas med knapparna inaktiverad med kontrolltypen som anges av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ButtonType%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ButtonType%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField>

trans-unit.source: It also sets the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebControl.Enabled%2A> property of the control to `false`.
